!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  so you see someone white to you, ya recon they know something about how to play there class but oh no they are a recent re birth in there 50s ick <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I like it the way it is, start from scratch, earn your second name, earn your levels.<br><br>Ona technical note, if the skills did not move over correctly you would be one sorry broken new player. Imagine having 100 defense at lvl 56 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Sorry to sound so negative, but this sounds a lot like allowing people to buy a hi level character because they cannot be bothered to play the lower levels. (ebay).<br><br>Perhaps there is something wrong with me that I like to earn my levels, and not be handed then.<br><br>Interesting idea not as bad as many I have had <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Hugs<br><br>Intra <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=dalninil>Dalninil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 124<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/23/02 2:22:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1176.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I have an idea... ^.~</span><hr size=1> the reason this isn't allowed..<br><br>oh we're doing Ixoblat everyone transform into mages..<br><br>we